Depending on your module implemention
you may need to add a nemo symlink in /usr/share/modules/modulefiles to
your $NEMO/modulefiles/nemo or a subdirectory nemo with named files to
your different nemo's, e.g.

     cd /usr/share/modules/modulefiles

     ln -s ~/NEMO/nemo/modulefiles/nemo    nemo

     mkdir nemo
     ln -s ~/NEMO/nemo/modulefiles/nemo    nemo/git
     ln -s ~/NEMO/nemo/modulefiles/nemo    nemo/git


See also ubuntu's environment-modules package, or install from ...
